*Spasao* je mnogo ljudi iz požara. (He saved many people from the fire.)

On je *spasao* sebe od odlaska u zatvor. (He saved himself from going to prison.)

Dirljiva priča o njemu koji je *spasao* živote u nesreći. (A touching story about him who saved lives in an accident.) 

Ona je *spasla* svoje dete. (She saved her child.)

*Spasilo* ga je dobre delo. (His good deed saved him.)